We awaken to a world where the future remains shrouded in uncertainty. Our vision cannot penetrate walls, the boundless expanse of the internet, nor the uncharted paths that lie ahead on our journey. Each day unfurls with its own set of trials and encounters, some of which leave us emotionally spent.

In the midst of this, there are those who opt to remain confined within the realms of man-made concrete, seeking refuge from life’s unpredictability. They choose the familiarity of these constructed structures over embracing the untamed beauty of God’s natural landscapes and the profound purity of His touch. To truly discover oneself, one must simply sit in a place devoid of distractions, allowing oneself to become attuned to their innermost being. #MINDofLARU #life #ocean #explore
